      <title>法国巴黎银行 (BNP) 客户将数十亿美元的 ESG 资金投入货币市场基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-28/bnp-s-clients-are-piling-esg-billions-into-money-market-funds</link>
